id: pm-ibp7
title: "Embedding timeout UX: improve ollama feedback for PM-CLI-A/9"
description: Recurring embedding timeouts with no progress feedback
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[3]: performance,sentry,vector-search
created_at: "2026-05-16T15:07:34.653Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-16T17:27:59.438Z"
author: claude-code-agent
resolution: Implemented search.embedding_timeout_ms and actionable embedding timeout diagnostics.
expected_result: Agents can tune semantic embedding timeout from project config and understand Ollama timeout remediation from the error text.
actual_result: "Timeout failures now include provider, model, batch_size, timeout_ms, and guidance to check provider availability, lower search.embedding_batch_size, raise search.embedding_timeout_ms, or use keyword search while indexing catches up."
