  "2026-05-16T17:27:39.714Z",codex-audit,"Evidence 2026-05-16: implemented configurable semantic embedding timeout via search.embedding_timeout_ms, propagated it into embedding batch requests, and made timeout failures include provider/model/batch_size/timeout_ms plus actionable guidance for local Ollama or slow providers. Verification passed: focused embedding/settings tests (24 tests), pm linked test run, isolated dogfood harness (44 workflows), health --refresh-vectors with vectorization ok and zero stale items, hybrid search probe, secret scan, and full release gate with 1309 tests at 100 percent coverage plus required Sentry/telemetry gate (Sentry critical=0 high=2; telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=2.32)."
